Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:02.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}いざ征け 光あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:12.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:18.64,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}星間に行く砦は唯一の安息地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:42.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}焦燥に打ち震え 所以には生と死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:47.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:52.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:02:00.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所へいざ集わんと 導かれしは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:07.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}志携えて 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:13.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}衛り継ぐ愛と 輝け命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:21.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}果敢に進む我ら シドニアの騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:01:02.57,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}踏上征途 光芒与我们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:35.98,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}穿梭星际的堡垒是唯一的安息之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:42.07,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}颤抖因焦躁而激发 生死于因果中存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:02:00.71,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}齐聚此地 接受引导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:07.00,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}众志成城 携手迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:13.40,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}满怀薪火相传的爱与灿烂的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:21.36,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}希德尼娅的骑士果敢前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:36.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:44.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:50.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:54.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:23:00.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:05.03,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:08.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:08.26,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.50,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:17.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:21.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:25.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:29.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:32.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:36.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:40.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:44.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:51.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:36.13,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界将要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.70,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果注定难逃死灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:44.70,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟该相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:50.70,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:54.40,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必体会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:23:00.33,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}这撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:05.03,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}响彻在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:08.26,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的镇魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.41,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.50,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然从飘乎的现实中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:17.85,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找寻你的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:21.45,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:25.18,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:29.43,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:32.47,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因为曾经深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:36.23,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:40.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}残留的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:44.15,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:51.08,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袋状结构破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测不到任何奇居子的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认融合个体䌷仍然存活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子刚才对我做了非常过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它们对我的朋友和同伴做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 希格斯粒子密度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 听话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科户濑机 严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇550的希格斯粒子密度急剧上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轨道在与䌷和科户濑机的接触点发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来人 去救䌷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 䌷她…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体整备班 至岐神开发厂区特殊培养槽集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船员医疗班 火速救治受伤的卫人操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重伤者送往高度紧急治疗室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻伤者送往医务局第三科或中央医院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 䌷她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在丧失了90%的身体组织
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把䌷恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前出击并回舰的机体中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前约有50%已完成整备并运回机库待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个融合个体又救了我们一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有她 我们肯定已经无家可归了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真是好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅和你都没事真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才打了那么场恶战啊 你就少计较点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 没想到你换成了义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是坚决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奶奶建议的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为组织再生要花很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手脚你很快就能适应的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还方便得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你挺精神的 我也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候可以出院？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说我了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷还没恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC99DCF&}给䌷姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}保护了希德尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H978FC9&}祝你能赶快好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢她的人有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之前好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转换炉管的第1024次定期清扫将按时进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次清扫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快点向䌷道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说战斗口粮换新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去试吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘移民舰是在放出先遣队后返航希德尼娅的途中遇袭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有人顺利到达七号行星就已经不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在大众合船正在逼近雷姆星系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很累的样子 估计是没怎么睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风他累了或者身体不舒服了也从来不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他的这一点很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也反而让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也认识一个和长道很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以常常很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看到他一个人承担太多东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是长道一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他一个人待一阵子 很快就会振作起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风长道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天也来看望䌷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷已经移到通常培养槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胞衣已经基本上完全复原 只等恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃相太难看了啦 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？星…白…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:11:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星 白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一不小心睡着了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷 谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 听说你醒了 我就把它带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我可以摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要温柔一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软软的 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.71,eyecatch,NTP,1020,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　无人小摊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.68,eyecatch,NTP,950,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　外周壁连接桥内部通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前希德尼娅与大众合船所在的位置之间隔着恒星雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们处于对方的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为按照计划进入雷姆星系 本舰将开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 继续保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在为外壳设置了专用的房间 让她在其中待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现有武器再加上䌷也还是敌不过大众合船的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长是另有妙计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过上一场战斗 融合个体反对派的势力已经大幅削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个东西怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就将进入第一次启动实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我转告由蕾博士 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 能看到外面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比之前的房间大了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢看书 所以小一点也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是觉得这里离居住区有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就一声不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我就是在刚才的䌷身上看到了一个人住在地下的她的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 去拜托缬让䌷能够进入居住区嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 进来一下说不定还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来现在重力就已经不稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发生事故怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别走那么快啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 从管理局那边拿到的地图上也是这么标的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又是这么黑漆漆的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我没事 赶紧往前走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅正面喷射口 已打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让工作队撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 行星九号的卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向喷射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布重力警报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅现在将开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将安全带扣在安全扶手上 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅现在将开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将安全带扣在安全扶手上 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道 刚才是不是有什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点了 再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向喷射 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面第一、第二喷射口 点火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种振动是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说起来今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷射已稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力场发生装置及平衡即将恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道 到外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是居住塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那整栋建筑里住着很多人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那里有好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多人 肯定也有很多种生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能变成人类的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去很多地方 结识很多人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该有多棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们每个人都知道你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没想过能亲眼见到这样的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的东西怎么会在走廊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,150,0,0,,{\an7}谷风长道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}今天是新训练生入住的日子，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}但是您的物品还未整理完毕。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}因此我们将其放到了门外。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}请见谅。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希德尼娅军总务科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不能再住宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不是在跟你说笑话啊 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比计划的要慢 所以我一直很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 义肢也需要调整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 有人来电了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 那我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长 长道 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 突然找你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能让我住一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶——？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
